dict.string:
:map - :
 :inoremap jj <esc>
 :map J 5j
 :map K 5k
 :nmap 0 ^
 :map Y y$
 :map <c-t> <esc>:tabnew<cr>
 :map <bs> gT
 :map <c-l> gt
 :let mapleader=" "
 :nnoremap <leader><leader> <C-^>
 :map <c-q> :q<CR>
 :map <leader>q :q<CR>
 :map <leader>w :w<CR>
 :noremap <leader>n <c-w><c-w>
 :noremap <leader>[ 20zh
 :noremap <leader>] 20zl
 :set expandtab tabstop=2 shiftwidth=2 autoindent smarttab
 :set incsearch ignorecase smartcase hlsearch
 :set hidden
 :set wildmenu
 :map <c-p> :e */**/*
 :inoremap <c-e> <end>
 :inoremap <c-f> <right>
 :inoremap <c-b> <left>
 :cnoremap <c-f> <right>
 :cnoremap <c-b> <left>
 :noremap <leader>n <c-w><c-w>
 :nmap <leader>`q :q!<CR>
 :nmap <leader>`w :wq<CR>
 :nmap <leader>`a :qa!<CR>
:set noerrorbells visualbell t_vb=
:echo 'Config loaded!'
